task.summary: Add unversioned files and updating modified
Add support for API level 26 (Android O)
Change launch screen styles for better color matching
Add listeners to perform download time calculations
Fix for issue #5 - App crashes on landscape
Close #3 - Add share option with intents to other apps
Add ripple effect to the CardView in activity_main layout
Improve supportLibrary dependencies values with extensions
